rackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Zig Zag-Fax']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/myam-james-2.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/james.jpg" alt="Myam James 2 / Kettel" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/myam-james-2.php">Myam James 2<br />Kettel</a></h4><p>優しい雰囲気を持ったエレクトロニカ音楽、アコースティック楽器がたくさん収録されているので疲れた心をリセットしてくれます。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0029S3RAQ?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0029S3RAQ" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Myam James 2-Kettel']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fmyam-james-2%252Fid314810505%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Myam James 2-Kettel']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/variance-vol-1-2.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/jega.jpg" alt="Variance, Vol. 1 & 2 / Jega" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/variance-vol-1-2.php">Variance, Vol. 1 & 2<br />Jega</a></h4><p>静粛な雰囲気を持った楽曲から、シンプルなビートのものまで様々なですが音色は統一されていてとても心地よい気分にさせてくれる1枚です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B002APNC30?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B002APNC30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Variance, Vol. 1 & 2-Jega']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fvariance-vol-1-2%252Fid322037567%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Variance, Vol. 1 & 2-Jega']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/radio-scarecrow.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/radioscare.jpg" alt="Radio Scarecrow / The Black Dog" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/radio-scarecrow.php">Radio Scarecrow<br />The Black Dog</a></h4><p>冷たい雰囲気を持ったダンスミュージックですが、その音色が心地よく体に響いてきます。夜に作業しながら聴きたくなる音楽。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B001437DGG?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B001437DGG" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'Radio Scarecrow-The Black Dog']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fradio-scarecrow%252Fid275518595%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'Radio Scarecrow-The Black Dog']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/polygon-cities.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/polygone.jpg" alt="polygon_Cities / Monolake" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/polygon-cities.php">polygon_Cities<br />Monolake</a></h4><p>とてもシンプルな音数の少ないサウンドで聴いていても圧迫感を感じさせません。深い夜にじっくりと聴いていたくなります。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B0009G01MC?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B0009G01MC" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'polygon_Cities-Monolake']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fpolygon-cities%252Fid73111591%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'polygon_Cities-Monolake']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl></div><div class="music-wrap clear"><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/a-certain-distance.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/certaindistance.jpg" alt="A Certain Distance / Lusine" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/a-certain-distance.php">A Certain Distance<br />Lusine</a></h4><p>ゆったりとしたダウンテンポミュージック。優しい音色が疲れた体に負担をかけません。心地よいリズムが素晴らしい作品です。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B002F3BQQC?ie=UTF8&tag=bootscafe-22&linkCode=as2&camp=247&creative=1211&creativeASIN=B002F3BQQC" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'Amazon', 'A Certain Distance-Lusine']);" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/amazon.gif" height="18" alt="amazonで買う" /></a>&nbsp;<a href="http%253A%252F%252Fitunes.apple.com%252Fjp%252Falbum%252Fa-certain-distance%252Fid326917421%253Fuo%253D4%2526partnerId%253D30" onClick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'iTunes', 'A Certain Distance-Lusine']);" name="submit" value="{$button_text['send']}" target="_blank"><img src="/common/img/parts/itunes.gif" height="18" alt="iTunesで買う" /></a></div></dd></dl><dl class="clear"><dt><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/foma.php"><img src="http://focussound.jp/review/upload/foma.jpg" alt="Foma / Lukid" /></a></dt><dd><h4><a href="http://focussound.jp/review/2010/09/foma.php">Foma<br />Lukid</a></h4><p>主張を抑えたBGMとしては最適の作品。音圧がありますが聴いていて苦しくなるようなものではなく、適度に刺激を与えてくれます。</p><div class="buy"><a href="http://www.amazon.co.jp/gp/product/B001ILDE6W?ie=UTF8&t